sequenceDiagram
    actor Patient
    participant Receptionist
    participant Nurse
    participant Episode
    participant VitalSign

    Patient->>Receptionist: Check-in
    Receptionist->>Nurse: Notify patient ready for vitals
    Nurse->>Nurse: Measure vital signs
    Note over Episode,VitalSign: VitalSign measurements are persisted and linked to the active Episode
    Nurse->>VitalSign: Associate with Episode
    VitalSign->>Episode: Linked